      "text": [
        " : «مَا زَارَنِي أَحَدٌ مِنْ أَوْلِيَائِي عَارِفاً بِحَقِّي إِلاَّ شُفِّعْتُ فِيهِ يَوْمَ اَلْقِيَامَةِ »."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.3184 - Al-Bazanti narrated from Imam Ali ibn Musa Ar-Ridha (as) who said:\n\"No one among my followers visits me, recognizing my right, except that I will intercede for them on the Day of Judgment.\""
        ]
